high_descs: Turn around and walk to the desk space on your left.
Pick up the pencil in front of the potted plant on the desk.
Turn around to walk across the room towards the nightstand next to the bed.
Set the pencil down on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil from the desk to the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the left side of the desk.
Pick up the pencil near the potted plant.
Turn around and walk ahead past the foot of the bed, then turn right and walk to the table to the table on the left side of the bed.
Place the pencil on the table to the left of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Place a pencil on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the white desk with a plant.
Pick up the pencil from the white desk in front of the plant.
Turn around and walk pass the bed then turn right, head to tan side table next to the bed.
Place the pencil on the tan side table next in front of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick the pencil up from the white desk and put it on the tan side table next to the bed.
